/* 伪装记账本：刻意平庸的冷灰蓝工具风——与解锁后的暖色世界形成最强反差 */
page {
  background: #F4F5F7;
  color: #333333;
  font-size: 28rpx;
  font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", sans-serif;
}

.ledger { padding: 24rpx; }

/* 汇总卡 */
.summary {
  background: #4977C4;
  border-radius: 16rpx;
  color: #FFFFFF;
  padding: 36rpx 32rpx;
}
.summary-label { font-size: 24rpx; opacity: 0.85; }
.summary-num { font-size: 64rpx; font-weight: 700; margin: 8rpx 0 4rpx; font-family: "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif; }
.summary-sub { font-size: 22rpx; opacity: 0.7; }

/* 表单 */
.form { background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 16rpx; margin-top: 24rpx; padding: 8rpx 28rpx 28rpx; }
.form-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  border-bottom: 1rpx solid #F0F1F3;
  padding: 24rpx 0;
}
.form-label { width: 120rpx; color: #666666; font-size: 26rpx; }
.form-input { flex: 1; font-size: 28rpx; }
.form-picker { flex: 1; }
.picker-value { font-size: 28rpx; color: #333333; }
.arrow { color: #BBBBBB; margin-left: 8rpx; }
.ph { color: #C2C6CC; }
.add-btn {
  margin-top: 28rpx;
  background: #4977C4;
  color: #FFFFFF;
  border-radius: 12rpx;
  font-size: 30rpx;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.add-btn::after { border: none; }

/* 流水 */
.list { background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 16rpx; margin-top: 24rpx; padding: 12rpx 28rpx; }
.list-title { font-size: 24rpx; color: #999999; padding: 16rpx 0 8rpx; }
.row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 22rpx 0;
  border-bottom: 1rpx solid #F5F6F8;
}
.row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.row-cat { font-size: 28rpx; color: #333333; }
.row-meta { font-size: 22rpx; color: #AAAAAA; margin-top: 4rpx; }
.row-amt { font-size: 30rpx; color: #333333; font-weight: 600; }

.foot { text-align: center; color: #C0C4CA; font-size: 22rpx; padding: 40rpx 0 20rpx; }
